snippet.title: Spaceflux | Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1344440/Spaceflux/
Spaceflux is a non-Euclidean online shooter in impossible geometry: fractal worlds, infinitely repeating space and fully destructible maps. 
EPILEPSY WARNING: THIS TRAILER CONTAINS BRIGHT FLASHING COLOURS.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Spaceflux1
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SpacefluxGame
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/spaceflux
https://spaceflux.net/

Special thanks to everyone who made the Kickstarter a huge success! https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/spaceflux/spaceflux-arena-fps-in-impossible-geometry
